  <num>41-162.06</num>
  <heading>Waiver of interest and penalty.</heading>
  <text>The Administrator:</text>
  <para>
    <num>(1)</num>
    <text>May waive, in whole or in part, interest under section 7075(a) and penalties under section 7075(b) or 7076; and</text>
  </para>
  <para>
    <num>(2)</num>
    <text>Shall waive a penalty under section 7075(b) if the Administrator determines that the holder acted in good faith and without negligence.</text>
  </para>
